# HUD::END_TEXT_COMMAND_OVERRIDE_BUTTON_TEXT

## Summary
Finishes what BEGIN_TEXT_COMMAND_OVERRIDE_BUTTON_TEXT started

## Parameters
* **INT** slot:
Index - which on-screen index to override after sorting.
Note the order is from RIGHT to LEFT.
